{"tid":2257571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鐵閘拆一起三 狂砍樹霸地 「沙螺灣國」拓車路冇王管","createTime":"2020-10-25T09:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T02:49:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8de1c91d7bf169d6c838298997a33d5f741f2558","tid":2257571,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201025/RE3AX7BPRBC2RJZWQ2EEATZUZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201025%2FRE3AX7BPRBC2RJZWQ2EEATZUZY%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=51634cfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201025%2FRE3AX7BPRBC2RJZWQ2EEATZUZY%2F&h=7e87e695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201025/RE3AX7BPRBC2RJZWQ2EEATZUZY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鐵閘拆一起三 狂砍樹霸地<br />\n「沙螺灣國」拓車路冇王管<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/79BgC4-x5yU8MIddoOvGh_RQrvc=/6897x5018/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AITMZ2Y46JFXLGKQYN55LTNVAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F79BgC4-x5yU8MIddoOvGh_RQrvc%3D%2F6897x5018%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAITMZ2Y46JFXLGKQYN55LTNVAU.jpg&h=d956fc25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10月1日除了是中共「國慶」，也是大嶼山沙螺灣村的「國慶」。當日村民鎖上大閘，截斷東澳古道，行山客望門興嘆。其實，「建國大業」早就開始，有人數月前開始佔用官地，擅自擴闊山徑行車。有保育團體早在上月初已向政府部門投訴，但官僚反應遲緩，任由「國道」成形。本報親探「沙螺灣國」現狀，發現「國道」行車已經通行無阻，王國卻越變越「獨立」，橫亘古道的鐵閘拆一起三，相當勇武。記者調查又發現，地產商早就囤積當區大批土地，國道的最大得益者，或許並非土生土長的村民。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：新地插旗 四年前掃路邊七地段<br />\n<br />\n記者：劉詩敏 關冠麒<br />\n<br />\n攝影：何量鈞<br />\n<br />\n東澳古道連接東涌和大澳，途經沙螺灣村、深石村和深屈等地，由東涌至深石村的一段，車輛過往無法通行，沙螺灣村對外交通只得渡輪。月初的封村事件，卻揭發了有人擅自擴闊公家路。<br />\n<br />\n為了解新開僻的車路狀況，記者嘗試找「藍的」由東涌經嶼南道駛往沙螺灣。但前。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者繼續步行前往沙螺灣村。由三山國王廟開始，本來完整的石屎路，變成新舊。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DygF5wtc41i8UY4rEA0M8ZP35rk=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/53T5Q5UXDFAHLA6DNLUFFTXF7I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDygF5wtc41i8UY4rEA0M8ZP35rk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F53T5Q5UXDFAHLA6DNLUFFTXF7I.jpg&h=bdf410ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■村內山徑被人擴闊，私家車可直接駛入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vf8WSmUatF18-emGBUVFAXTjxSw=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WI36HWSCVVDNNAQP54DJNII5WY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvf8WSmUatF18-emGBUVFAXTjxSw%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWI36HWSCVVDNNAQP54DJNII5WY.jpg&h=465a625f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■村民疑非法開墾農地，更用木材自製圍欄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立「私人重地」牌拒遊人<br />\n<br />\n接近沙螺灣村，部份新開僻的路面仍未鋪上石屎，只有黃泥地。有山坡被整塊削走，斜坡保護網被剪走，遺下大量木頭和廢料。沿路至少有十數個避車或泊車處，相信同樣靠砍伐樹木夷平土地而成。政府的反制措施卻似乎只有豎立多塊「政府土地」告示牌在路旁。<br />\n<br />\n抵達沙螺灣村後，記者重遇由深石村駛入的銀色私家車，換言之，沙螺灣往來羌山、嶼。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雖然對外交通靠強行開路獲得改善，但沙螺灣村反變得不想對外交流，儼如「獨立王國」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n過去兩年，沙螺灣村曾兩度和藝術團體「誇啦啦藝術集匯」合辦藝術節，當。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n平日留在沙螺灣村的居民稀少。原居民張先生對非法開墾車路的質疑沒有直接承認，只表示。。。。。。。。。。。。」。<br />\n<br />\n守護大嶼聯盟召集人謝世傑早在今年8月尾已收到非法開路的舉報，當時沙螺灣村。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他批評當局執法不力，「踢一腳先行半步」。他又質疑開路接駁救護服務的說法，「𠵱家私家車出出入入，死咗火停喺中間咪又係阻救護服務，根本自打嘴巴」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有村民向他表示車輛出入令路段變得危險，開路並非所有村民的共識，「又話遊客（踏）風火輪，喺呢條路揸車又安全啲咩？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D6SQZb5RKXt72LYw11g8nPcVMMQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H3YHCMEVSNF3JMIRAETTPZYJZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD6SQZb5RKXt72LYw11g8nPcVMMQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH3YHCMEVSNF3JMIRAETTPZYJZM.jpg&h=b6fde5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■深石村進入沙螺灣村口路段，被人加裝了鐵閘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5xh9_7BO7Mlc2TB36hke8Me3wcw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AGLHT6UERVH2VC7OZ3JRH3GJHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5xh9_7BO7Mlc2TB36hke8Me3wcw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAGLHT6UERVH2VC7OZ3JRH3GJHQ.jpg&h=22ede7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有政府土地疑被非法佔用，閘外設有電錶，大片樹木被夷平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n環團憂影響蝴蝶生態<br />\n<br />\n長春社公共事務經理吳希文直指被開墾的路段「好誇張，完全面目全非」，而深石及沙螺灣村一帶的環境與蝴蝶熱點䃟頭相似，大規模砍伐木林會影響當地蝴蝶生態。他認為政府應勒令相關人士修復路段，並以「發展審批地區圖」加強管制其發展，根據《城市規劃條例》檢控非法開墾人士。<br />\n<br />\n地政總署回覆稱，接獲有人非法擴建通道及佔用政府土地的投訴後，曾多次視察。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者先後前往沙螺灣村村長李秀梅的住處及位於荃灣的辦公室邀約訪問，但至截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ELPGqagdmV36pyswspu00W7JsAI=/2277x4860/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LLVGUVKCOFFQLLGZ6GXXQ7DCVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FELPGqagdmV36pyswspu00W7JsAI%3D%2F2277x4860%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLLVGUVKCOFFQLLGZ6GXXQ7DCVA.jpg&h=1253b44a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16d05483da98b71107c90f02118c1b8c8b98d8e5","tid":2257571,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:28:20.000Z","msg":"佔山為王 咁你咪好威威"},{"pid":"81ff661c03976ea1b7f77905de96a1e23c60043f","tid":2257571,"uid":286155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"國務院堅決反對一切分裂中國的圖謀及行徑，堅決反對任何外部勢力干涉，以任何形式，把任何一塊中國領土由中國分裂出去。 <br 